description.en: Vcash is a cryptocurrency that uses a multitier architecture that enables the coin to scale better in a secure way. The lead developer goes under the name of John Connor. There is no pre-mine, pre-sale, IPO or ICO for Vcash. Vcash was previously known as Vanillacoin.
